    public class DBTestActivity
extends android.support.v7.app.AppCompatActivity
    DBTestActivity is basically just an activity made as a practical application of the functions implemented in DBManager, testing to make sure they are all functioning correctly. Most, if not all, of this is placeholder code that is unlikely to appear in the final product.
